CustomField.description: This option allows you to display more details in the drop down list when selecting a Package Profile for ReUse in the Shipping Wizard. This drop down list only appears on Package section of the Shipping Wizard if a saved Package for ReUse exists.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This option allows you to display more details in the drop down list when selecting a Package Profile for ReUse in the Shipping Wizard. This drop down list only appears on Package section of the Shipping Wizard if a saved Package for ReUse exists.
CustomField.label: Detailed View - ReUse Package List
